(40, 25, 6, 19, 98, 9, 9, 'the bridegroom cometh', 'Judgment and Arrival of the Lord', 'This connection highlights the theme of the Lord''s coming, as both passages reference the arrival of the Lord or bridegroom. Matthew 25:6 speaks of the bridegroom coming, while Psalms 98:9 emphasizes the Lord coming to judge the earth.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
